    "description": "从屡获殊荣的游戏 —— Stories: The Path of Destinies 的研发团队手中，再次创造了Omensight，一个崭新的动作皆谋杀侦探式游戏。<br><br>你是先驱者，只在危机时期才出现的神话战士。乌拉利亚的土地被战争撕裂了。但更糟糕的是：当夜幕降临时，你将目睹世界被一个黑暗之神毁灭。<br><br>你有能力重复末日当天的事故。通过领导调查，与末日有关的角色一起互动，跟他们合作或者作战，并运用 Omensight 的能力来量新编织新的叙述。<br><br>通过你的决定，技能和智慧，你可以改变当天的过程，也许能为更光明的未来铺路。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/455820/extras/3668dbe58cddea587cceaa4cf337a88f.webp?t=1706386498\" width=600 height=51 /></span><br><br>游戏还有 Patricia Summersett（<i>塞尔达传说：旷野之息</i>）和 Julian Casey（<i>We Happy Few</i>）等顶尖配音演员的参与，以及一组优秀的编剧团队， 包括 Nadim Boukhira（<i>Stories</i>），Genese Davis（<i>The Holder's Dominion</i>）和 Chris Avellone （<i>异域镇魂曲：折磨</i>）“ 等成员。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/455820/extras/b43c21efa013dd6fcf53d3f2471dc8ca.avif?t=1706386498\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/455820/extras/b5bd06d9b90f5da915276c7f2f90f2a4.avif?t=1706386498\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/455820/extras/04128e358cbdb681c72ad2c60dfe1de6.avif?t=1706386498\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/455820/extras/eda4e91ba123e4b72c7d2ab2d157291d.avif?t=1706386498\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/455820/extras/05b4b1a3deca36f88660baaa1577a7d5.webp?t=1706386498\" width=600 height=51 /></span>",
